text: Amna Riaz is a Pakistani female YouTuber and food expert who is known for her channel Kitchen with Amna. She is the first Pakistani women to achieve Gold Play Button. She started her channel in 2016 and subsequently uploaded her first video as a test. She teaches beginners complex Pakistani dishes in short and simple videos. She was born in Lahore, Pakistan to a Kashmiri family. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Pakistani YouTubers Category:People from Lahore Category:Pakistani people of Kashmiri descent Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
